reviewText: There are three videos in this disk,The first movie is with Rydia from Final Fantasy IV having sex probably with Cecil,the second movie is with Yuna from Final Fantasy X having sex with who knows who,this one is kinda slow but still good animation,the third movie is with Tifa from Final Fantasy VII having sex with some kind of "Blue Ghost".All three videos look good,not great,but good,I myself liked it,for me this disk is more like "Fan Service" for some people who like to see Final Fantasy Girls naked,in my opinion,I recommend buying it!.
